INSERT INTO SGT_PROVIDER_REPORT_PAYMENT ( SUBSYSTEM_ID, SUBSYSTEM_VALUE, SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID, PERSON_ID, PROVIDER_ORG_ID, PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID, EFFECTIVE_DATE, AMOUNT,PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID, BATCH_REQUEST_ID, CREATED_BY, CREATED_DATE, MODIFIED_BY, MODIFIED_DATE, UPDATE_SEQ ) SELECT 349 AS SUBSYSTEM_ID, 'PMNT' AS SUBSYSTEM_VALUE, SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID, PERSON_ID, PROVIDER_ORG_ID, PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID, EFFECTIVE_DATE, AMOUNT, PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID, NULL AS BATCH_REQUEST_ID, 'PERSLink Batch'+' '+ convert(nvarchar,@batchscheduleid) AS CREATED_BY, GETDATE() AS CREATED_DATE, 'PERSLink Batch'+' '+ convert(nvarchar,@batchscheduleid) AS MODIFIED_BY, GETDATE() AS MODIFIED_DATE, 0 AS UPDATE_SEQ FROM ( SELECT DTL.*,PPIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID FROM( SELECT PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL_ID AS SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID ,PHH.PERSON_ID, PHD.VENDOR_ORG_ID AS PROVIDER_ORG_ID, PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID, PAYMENT_DATE AS EFFECTIVE_DATE, PIT.ITEM_TYPE_CODE, SUM(PHD.AMOUNT * PIT.item_type_direction * -1) AS AMOUNT FROM SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL PHD WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER PHH WITH(NOLOCK) ON PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT PA WITH(NOLOCK) ON PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID AND isnull(PHH.ORG_ID,0) = isnull(PA.PAYEE_ORG_ID,0) and ISNULL(PHH.PERSON_ID,0) = ISNULL(PA.PAYEE_PERSLINK_ID,0) INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PIT WITH(NOLOCK) ON PHD.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = PIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID WHERE PHH.PAYMENT_SCHEDULE_ID = @PAYMENTSCHEDULEID AND PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID IS NOT NULL AND PA.BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE NOT IN('DBCT','DTCT','DBDC','DBTT','SPEL') AND PHD.VENDOR_ORG_ID IS NOT NULL AND DEDUCTION_VALUE <> 'RONL' AND PIT.UPDATE_PROVIDER_REPORT_PAYMENT_FLAG = 'Y' GROUP BY PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL_ID, PHH.PERSON_ID, PHD.VENDOR_ORG_ID, PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID, PIT.ITEM_TYPE_CODE, PAYMENT_DATE)DTL INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV (NOLOCK) ON CV.CODE_ID=2518 AND DTL.ITEM_TYPE_CODE=CV.DATA1 INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PPIT (NOLOCK) ON PPIT.ITEM_TYPE_CODE=CV.DATA2
UNION ALL --26652 SELECT DTL.*,PPIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID FROM( SELECT PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL_ID AS SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID ,PHH.PERSON_ID, PHD.VENDOR_ORG_ID AS PROVIDER_ORG_ID, PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID, PAYMENT_DATE AS EFFECTIVE_DATE, PIT.ITEM_TYPE_CODE, SUM(PHD.AMOUNT * PIT.item_type_direction * -1) AS AMOUNT FROM SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL PHD WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER PHH WITH(NOLOCK) ON PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PIT WITH(NOLOCK) ON PHD.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = PIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID WHERE PHH.PAYMENT_SCHEDULE_ID = @PAYMENTSCHEDULEID AND PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID IS NULL AND PHD.VENDOR_ORG_ID IS NOT NULL AND DEDUCTION_VALUE <> 'RONL' AND PIT.UPDATE_PROVIDER_REPORT_PAYMENT_FLAG = 'Y' GROUP BY PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL_ID, PHH.PERSON_ID, PHD.VENDOR_ORG_ID, PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID, PIT.ITEM_TYPE_CODE, PAYMENT_DATE)DTL INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV (NOLOCK) ON CV.CODE_ID=2518 AND DTL.ITEM_TYPE_CODE=CV.DATA1 INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PPIT (NOLOCK) ON PPIT.ITEM_TYPE_CODE=CV.DATA2
UNION ALL
SELECT DTL.*,PPIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID FROM( SELECT PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL_ID AS SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID ,PA.PAYEE_PERSLINK_ID, PHD.VENDOR_ORG_ID AS PROVIDER_ORG_ID, PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID, PAYMENT_DATE AS EFFECTIVE_DATE, PIT.ITEM_TYPE_CODE, SUM(PHD.AMOUNT * PIT.item_type_direction * -1) AS AMOUNT FROM SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL PHD WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER PHH WITH(NOLOCK) ON PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT PA WITH(NOLOCK) ON PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ROLLOVER_DETAIL PARD WITH(NOLOCK) ON PARD.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID AND ISNULL(PHH.ORG_ID,0) = ISNULL(PARD.ROLLOVER_ORG_ID,0) INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PIT WITH(NOLOCK) ON PHD.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = PIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID WHERE PHH.PAYMENT_SCHEDULE_ID = @PAYMENTSCHEDULEID AND PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID IS NOT NULL AND PA.BENEFIT_OPTION_VALUE NOT IN('DBCT','DTCT','DBDC','DBTT','SPEL') AND PHD.VENDOR_ORG_ID IS NOT NULL AND DEDUCTION_VALUE <> 'RONL' AND PIT.UPDATE_PROVIDER_REPORT_PAYMENT_FLAG = 'Y' AND PARD.ROLLOVER_TYPE_VALUE = 'RIRA' GROUP BY PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL_ID, PA.PAYEE_PERSLINK_ID, PHD.VENDOR_ORG_ID, PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID, PIT.ITEM_TYPE_CODE, PAYMENT_DATE)DTL INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV (NOLOCK) ON CV.CODE_ID=2518 AND DTL.ITEM_TYPE_CODE=CV.DATA1 INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PPIT (NOLOCK) ON PPIT.ITEM_TYPE_CODE=CV.DATA2 ) AS TEMP

INSERT INTO SGT_PROVIDER_REPORT_PAYMENT ( SUBSYSTEM_ID, SUBSYSTEM_VALUE, SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID, PERSON_ID, PROVIDER_ORG_ID, PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID, EFFECTIVE_DATE, AMOUNT,PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID, BATCH_REQUEST_ID, CREATED_BY, CREATED_DATE, MODIFIED_BY, MODIFIED_DATE, UPDATE_SEQ ) SELECT 349 AS SUBSYSTEM_ID, 'PMNT' AS SUBSYSTEM_VALUE, SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID, PERSON_ID, PROVIDER_ORG_ID, PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID, EFFECTIVE_DATE, AMOUNT, PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID, NULL AS BATCH_REQUEST_ID, 'PERSLink Batch'+' '+ convert(nvarchar,@batchscheduleid) AS CREATED_BY, GETDATE() AS CREATED_DATE, 'PERSLink Batch'+' '+ convert(nvarchar,@batchscheduleid) AS MODIFIED_BY, GETDATE() AS MODIFIED_DATE, 0 AS UPDATE_SEQ FROM ( SELECT DTL.*,PPIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID FROM( SELECT PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL_ID AS SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID ,PHH.PERSON_ID, PHD.VENDOR_ORG_ID AS PROVIDER_ORG_ID, PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID, PAYMENT_DATE AS EFFECTIVE_DATE, PIT.ITEM_TYPE_CODE, SUM(PHD.AMOUNT * PIT.item_type_direction * -1) AS AMOUNT FROM SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL PHD INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER PHH ON PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT PA ON PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID AND isnull(PHH.ORG_ID,0) = isnull(PA.PAYEE_ORG_ID,0) and ISNULL(PHH.PERSON_ID,0) = ISNULL(PA.PAYEE_PERSLINK_ID,0) INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PIT ON PHD.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = PIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID WHERE PHH.PAYMENT_SCHEDULE_ID = @PAYMENTSCHEDULEID AND PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID IS NOT NULL AND PHD.VENDOR_ORG_ID IS NOT NULL AND DEDUCTION_VALUE <> 'RONL' AND PIT.UPDATE_PROVIDER_REPORT_PAYMENT_FLAG = 'Y' GROUP BY PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL_ID, PHH.PERSON_ID, PHD.VENDOR_ORG_ID, PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID, PIT.ITEM_TYPE_CODE, PAYMENT_DATE)DTL INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV (NOLOCK) ON CV.CODE_ID=2518 AND DTL.ITEM_TYPE_CODE=CV.DATA1 INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PPIT (NOLOCK) ON PPIT.ITEM_TYPE_CODE=CV.DATA2 UNION ALL
SELECT DTL.*,PPIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID FROM( SELECT PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL_ID AS SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID ,PA.PAYEE_PERSLINK_ID, PHD.VENDOR_ORG_ID AS PROVIDER_ORG_ID, PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID, PAYMENT_DATE AS EFFECTIVE_DATE, PIT.ITEM_TYPE_CODE, SUM(PHD.AMOUNT * PIT.item_type_direction * -1) AS AMOUNT FROM SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL PHD INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER PHH ON PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT PA ON PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ROLLOVER_DETAIL PARD ON PARD.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID AND isnull(PHH.ORG_ID,0) = ISNULL(PARD.ROLLOVER_ORG_ID,0) INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PIT ON PHD.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = PIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID WHERE PHH.PAYMENT_SCHEDULE_ID = @PAYMENTSCHEDULEID AND PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID IS NOT NULL AND PHD.VENDOR_ORG_ID IS NOT NULL AND DEDUCTION_VALUE <> 'RONL' AND PIT.UPDATE_PROVIDER_REPORT_PAYMENT_FLAG = 'Y' AND PARD.ROLLOVER_TYPE_VALUE = 'RIRA' GROUP BY PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL_ID, PA.PAYEE_PERSLINK_ID, PHD.VENDOR_ORG_ID, PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID, PIT.ITEM_TYPE_CODE, PAYMENT_DATE)DTL INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE CV (NOLOCK) ON CV.CODE_ID=2518 AND DTL.ITEM_TYPE_CODE=CV.DATA1 INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PPIT (NOLOCK) ON PPIT.ITEM_TYPE_CODE=CV.DATA2 ) AS TEMP

SELECT ISNULL(PRP.PROVIDER_ORG_ID,0) PROVIDER_ORG_ID, ISNULL(BA.PLAN_ID,0) PLAN_ID, CASE WHEN ORG.ACH_ACCOUNT_NUMBER IS NOT NULL THEN ORG.ACH_ACCOUNT_NUMBER ELSE ISNULL(ORG.ORG_CODE,'') END AS ORG_CODE, ISNULL(ORG.ORG_NAME,'') ORG_NAME, ISNULL(SUM(PRP.AMOUNT),0) CONTRIBUTION_AMOUNT, 'A' AS PAYMENT_OPTION_VALUE FROM SGT_PROVIDER_REPORT_PAYMENT PRP INNER JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG ON ORG.ORG_ID=PRP.PROVIDER_ORG_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT PA ON PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID=PRP.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION BA ON PA.APPLICATION_ID=BA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_ID INNER JOIN SGT_ORG_BANK OB ON OB.USAGE_VALUE = 'DEP' AND OB.STATUS_VALUE = 'ACTV' AND OB.ORG_ID=PRP.PROVIDER_ORG_ID WHERE PRP.BATCH_REQUEST_ID IS NULL AND PRP.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @PAYMENTDATE GROUP BY PRP.PROVIDER_ORG_ID,BA.PLAN_ID,ORG.ORG_CODE,ORG.ORG_NAME,payment_option_value, CASE WHEN ORG.ACH_ACCOUNT_NUMBER IS NOT NULL THEN ORG.ACH_ACCOUNT_NUMBER ELSE ISNULL(ORG.ORG_CODE,'') END
select * from sgt_provider_report_payment a inner join sgt_organization b on a.prvoder_org_id=b.org_id where BATCH_REQUEST_ID is null

SELECT A.PROVIDER_ORG_ID,SUM(AMOUNT) AS AMOUNT FROM SGT_PROVIDER_REPORT_PAYMENT A WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PROVIDER_REPORT_DATA_BATCH_REQUEST B WITH(NOLOCK) ON A.PROVIDER_ORG_ID=B.ORG_ID WHERE A.BATCH_REQUEST_ID IS NULL AND B.ORG_ID= (SELECT ORG_ID FROM SGT_ORGANIZATION WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE ORG_CODE= (SELECT DATA1 FROM SGS_CODE_VALUE WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE CODE_ID=52 AND CODE_VALUE='STCM')) AND B.STATUS_VALUE = 'NTPR' AND A.EFFECTIVE_DATE BETWEEN B.EFFECTIVE_START_DATE AND B.EFFECTIVE_END_DATE GROUP BY A.PROVIDER_ORG_ID

Select distinct a.* from sgt_provider_report_payment a (nolock) inner join sgt_organization org (nolock) on a.provider_org_id=org.org_id inner join sgt_payment_history_header phh(nolock) on phh.org_id=a.provider_org_id inner join sgt_payment_history_detail phd(nolock) on phh.payment_history_header_id=phd.payment_history_header_id and a.payment_item_type_id=phd.payment_item_type_id where a.batch_request_id is null and phh.payment_schedule_id=@batchscheduleid and org.org_code <> (select data1 from sgs_code_value where code_id=52 and code_value='STCM') and a.effective_date <= @paymentdate

select * from sgt_provider_report_payment a WITH(NOLOCK) inner join sgt_provider_report_data_batch_request b WITH(NOLOCK) on a.provider_org_id=b.org_id where a.batch_request_id is null and b.org_id= (select org_id from sgt_organization WITH(NOLOCK) where org_code= (select data1 from sgs_code_value WITH(NOLOCK) where code_id=52 and code_value='STCM')) AND A.EFFECTIVE_DATE BETWEEN B.EFFECTIVE_START_DATE AND B.EFFECTIVE_END_DATE

SELECT ORG_NAME AS ORGANIZATION_NAME, ISNULL(LAST_NAME,'')+' '+ISNULL(FIRST_NAME,'')+', '+ISNULL(MIDDLE_NAME,'') AS LAST_NAME, FIRST_NAME, PAPIT.ACCOUNT_NUMBER, SUM(PRP.AMOUNT) AS AMOUNT FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT(NOLOCK) PA INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER(NOLOCK) PHH ON PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL(NOLOCK) PHD ON PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE(NOLOCK) PIT ON PHD.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = PIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PROVIDER_REPORT_PAYMENT(NOLOCK) PRP ON SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID = PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL_ID AND SUBSYSTEM_ID = 349 AND SUBSYSTEM_VALUE = 'PMNT' INNER JOIN DBO.SGT_ORGANIZATION(NOLOCK) ORG ON PRP.PROVIDER_ORG_ID = ORG.ORG_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON(NOLOCK) PER ON PA.PAYEE_PERSLINK_ID = PER.PERSON_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PAPIT(NOLOCK) ON PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PAPIT.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID AND PHD.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = PAPIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID WHERE PHH.PAYMENT_DATE = @PAYMENTDATE AND PAYMENT_SCHEDULE_ID IN ( SELECT PAYMENT_SCHEDULE_ID FROM SGT_PAYMENT_SCHEDULE WHERE PAYMENT_DATE = @PAYMENTDATE AND STATUS_VALUE = 'PRCD' ) AND UPPER(CHECK_COMPONENT_DESCRIPTION) = 'CHILD SUPPORT' GROUP BY ORG_NAME, LAST_NAME, FIRST_NAME, PAPIT.ACCOUNT_NUMBER,MIDDLE_NAME ORDER BY ORG_NAME, LAST_NAME

SELECT ORG_NAME AS ORGANIZATION_NAME, ISNULL(LAST_NAME,'')+' '+ISNULL(FIRST_NAME,'')+', '+ISNULL(MIDDLE_NAME,'') AS LAST_NAME, FIRST_NAME, RIGHT(SSN,4) SSN, SUM(PRP.AMOUNT) AS DUES_AMOUNT FROM DBO.SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT(NOLOCK) PA INNER JOIN DBO.SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER(NOLOCK) PHH ON PHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN DBO.SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL(NOLOCK) PHD ON PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN DBO.SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE(NOLOCK) PIT ON PHD.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = PIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PROVIDER_REPORT_PAYMENT PRP ON SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID = PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL_ID AND SUBSYSTEM_ID = 349 AND SUBSYSTEM_VALUE = 'PMNT' INNER JOIN DBO.SGT_ORGANIZATION(NOLOCK) ORG ON PRP.PROVIDER_ORG_ID = ORG.ORG_ID INNER JOIN DBO.SGT_PERSON(NOLOCK) PER ON PA.PAYEE_PERSLINK_ID = PER.PERSON_ID WHERE PHH.PAYMENT_DATE = @PAYMENTDATE AND PAYMENT_SCHEDULE_ID IN ( SELECT PAYMENT_SCHEDULE_ID FROM SGT_PAYMENT_SCHEDULE WHERE PAYMENT_DATE = @PAYMENTDATE AND STATUS_VALUE = 'PRCD' ) AND UPPER(CHECK_COMPONENT_DESCRIPTION) = 'DUES' GROUP BY ORG_NAME, LAST_NAME, FIRST_NAME, RIGHT(SSN,4), MIDDLE_NAME ORDER BY ORG_NAME, LAST_NAME

SELECT ORG_NAME AS ORGANIZATION_NAME, ISNULL(LAST_NAME,'')+' '+ISNULL(FIRST_NAME,'')+', '+ISNULL(MIDDLE_NAME,'') AS LAST_NAME, FIRST_NAME, PRP.ACCOUNT_NUMBER as ACCOUNT_NUMBER, RIGHT(SSN,4) SSN, SUM(PRP.AMOUNT) AS DUES_AMOUNT FROM SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER(NOLOCK) PHH INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL(NOLOCK) PHD ON PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE(NOLOCK) PIT ON PHD.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = PIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID INNER JOIN (SELECT PRP1.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,PRP1.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID, PAPIT.ACCOUNT_NUMBER,sum(PRP1.AMOUNT) AS AMOUNT FROM SGT_PROVIDER_REPORT_PAYMENT(NOLOCK) PRP1 INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL(NOLOCK) PHD1 on PRP1.SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID = PHD1.PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER(NOLOCK) PHH1 ON PHD1.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHH1.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PIT1 ON PHD1.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = PIT1.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PAPIT(NOLOCK) ON PRP1.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PAPIT.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID and PHD1.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = PAPIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID AND PRP1.PROVIDER_ORG_ID = PAPIT.VENDOR_ORG_ID WHERE (UPPER(PIT1.CHECK_COMPONENT_DESCRIPTION) like '%CHILD%SUPPORT%' ) AND PHH1.PAYMENT_DATE BETWEEN PAPIT.START_DATE AND (CASE WHEN PAPIT.END_DATE IS NULL THEN '99991231' ELSE PAPIT.END_DATE END) group by PRP1.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,PRP1.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID,PAPIT.ACCOUNT_NUMBER ) AS PRP ON PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PRP.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN DBO.SGT_ORGANIZATION(NOLOCK) ORG ON PHH.ORG_ID = ORG.ORG_ID inner join sgt_payee_account pa on pa.payee_account_id = prp.payee_account_id INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON(NOLOCK) PER ON PA.PAYEE_PERSLINK_ID = PER.PERSON_ID WHERE PHH.PAYMENT_DATE = @PAYMENTDATE AND (UPPER(CHECK_COMPONENT_DESCRIPTION) like '%CHILD%SUPPORT%' ) and PHH.PAYMENT_SCHEDULE_ID=@PAYMENTSCHEDULEID GROUP BY ORG_NAME, LAST_NAME, FIRST_NAME, MIDDLE_NAME, RIGHT(SSN,4),PRP.ACCOUNT_NUMBER ORDER BY ORG_NAME, LAST_NAME

SELECT ORG_NAME AS ORGANIZATION_NAME, ISNULL(LAST_NAME,'')+' '+ISNULL(FIRST_NAME,'')+', '+ISNULL(MIDDLE_NAME,'') AS LAST_NAME, FIRST_NAME, PRP.ACCOUNT_NUMBER as ACCOUNT_NUMBER, RIGHT(SSN,4) SSN, SUM(PRP.AMOUNT) AS DUES_AMOUNT FROM SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER(NOLOCK) PHH INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL(NOLOCK) PHD ON PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE(NOLOCK) PIT ON PHD.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = PIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID INNER JOIN (SELECT PRP1.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,PRP1.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID, PAPIT.ACCOUNT_NUMBER,sum(PRP1.AMOUNT) AS AMOUNT FROM SGT_PROVIDER_REPORT_PAYMENT(NOLOCK) PRP1 INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL(NOLOCK) PHD1 on PRP1.SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID = PHD1.PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER(NOLOCK) PHH1 ON PHD1.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHH1.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PIT1 ON PHD1.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = PIT1.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PAPIT(NOLOCK) ON PRP1.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PAPIT.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID and PHD1.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = PAPIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID AND PRP1.PROVIDER_ORG_ID = PAPIT.VENDOR_ORG_ID WHERE (UPPER(PIT1.CHECK_COMPONENT_DESCRIPTION) like '%DUES%' ) AND PHH1.PAYMENT_DATE BETWEEN PAPIT.START_DATE AND (CASE WHEN PAPIT.END_DATE IS NULL THEN '99991231' ELSE PAPIT.END_DATE END) group by PRP1.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,PRP1.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID,PAPIT.ACCOUNT_NUMBER ) AS PRP ON PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PRP.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN DBO.SGT_ORGANIZATION(NOLOCK) ORG ON PHH.ORG_ID = ORG.ORG_ID inner join sgt_payee_account pa on pa.payee_account_id = prp.payee_account_id INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON(NOLOCK) PER ON PA.PAYEE_PERSLINK_ID = PER.PERSON_ID WHERE PHH.PAYMENT_DATE = @PAYMENTDATE AND (UPPER(CHECK_COMPONENT_DESCRIPTION) like '%DUES%' ) and PHH.PAYMENT_SCHEDULE_ID=@PAYMENTSCHEDULEID GROUP BY ORG_NAME, LAST_NAME, FIRST_NAME, MIDDLE_NAME, RIGHT(SSN,4),PRP.ACCOUNT_NUMBER ORDER BY ORG_NAME, LAST_NAME

select o.org_code,o.org_name,c.item_type_description as item_type,a.amount from sgt_payment_history_detail a inner join sgt_payment_item_type c on a.payment_item_type_id=c.payment_item_type_id inner join sgt_payment_history_header b on a.payment_history_header_id=b.payment_history_header_id inner join sgt_organization o on b.org_id=o.org_id where b.payment_schedule_id=@paymentscheduleid

SELECT C.DESCRIPTION AS TRANSACTION_TYPE , A.PERSON_ID, CASE WHEN A.PERSON_ID > 0 THEN (ISNULL(B.LAST_NAME, '') +' '+ ISNULL(B.FIRST_NAME, '') +' '+ ISNULL(B.MIDDLE_NAME, '')) ELSE RESULT.NAME END AS NAME, SUM(A.AMOUNT) AS AMOUNT, RESULT.ORG_CODE FROM SGT_PROVIDER_REPORT_PAYMENT A WITH(NOLOCK) LEFT JOIN SGT_PERSON B WITH(NOLOCK) ON A.PERSON_ID = B.PERSON_ID INNER JOIN SGS_CODE_VALUE C WITH(NOLOCK) ON A.SUBSYSTEM_ID = C.CODE_ID AND A.SUBSYSTEM_VALUE = C.CODE_VALUE INNER JOIN (SELECT (CASE WHEN PHH.PERSON_ID IS NULL THEN ORG.ORG_CODE END) AS ORG_CODE, PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL_ID, ORG.ORG_NAME AS NAME FROM SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER PHH WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL PHD WITH(NOLOCK) ON PHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID = PHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID LEFT JOIN SGT_ORGANIZATION ORG WITH(NOLOCK) ON PHH.ORG_ID = ORG.ORG_ID )RESULT ON RESULT.PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL_ID = A.SUBSYSTEM_REF_ID WHERE BATCH_REQUEST_ID = @BATCHREQUESTID AND PROVIDER_ORG_ID = @IRSORGID GROUP BY C.DESCRIPTION , A.PERSON_ID, ISNULL(B.LAST_NAME, '') +' '+ ISNULL(B.FIRST_NAME, '') +' '+ ISNULL(B.MIDDLE_NAME, '') , RESULT.ORG_CODE, RESULT.NAME ORDER BY C.DESCRIPTION , ISNULL(B.LAST_NAME, '') +' '+ ISNULL(B.FIRST_NAME, '') +' '+ ISNULL(B.MIDDLE_NAME, '')
